Consumers are being urged to return certain Dark and Lovely Precise Diamond Hair Relaxer to stores. Manufacturer, L'Oreal, recalled the product after at least 22 consumers laid complaints. #eNCA speaks to Consumer Commission's Prudence Moilwa. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Consumers are being urged to return certain Dark and Lovely Precise Diamond Hair Relaxers to stores. Manufacturer, L'Oreal, recalled the product after at least 22 consumers laid complaints. READ: Product recall | Consumers urged to return frozen vegetables The Consumer Commission says the products may lead to increased hair breakage and scalp irritation. The company says the imbalance of the active raw material has affected 2 batches of the 125ml tubs. Watch the video above for more details.